Description: Replication package for studies examining the impacts of rating revisions in United States agricultural insurance.
  - Actuarial Impacts of Rating Revisions in United States Agricultural Insurance.
  - Actuarial Updates and Taxpayer Costs in Subsidized Agricultural Insurance Programs.
  - The Effect of Actuarial Updates on Private-to-Public Risk Transfers in Agricultural Insurance.
